To create a vg with customized PE size:
=======================================

# vgcreate  -s <size of PE( 1-128)> <name for the vg > <pv names> 

# lvcreate â€“l <no of LE> -n <name for the LV> <volume group name> 

OS installation with LVM

rootlv	17Gb - 17408
varlv	10Gb - 10240
tmplv	5Gb - 5120
optlv	3Gb - 3072
homelv	2Gb - 2048
boot	1Gb - 1024
swap	2Gb - 2048

